{"tid":1268352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係黑社會嚟 唔係民意 唔使太過在乎","createTime":"2019-06-30T09:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T11:13:10.000Z","uid":45206,"like":229,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ea874d31f3ee0523011b9c9b341be69e169e4a87","tid":1268352,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"佔中嗰時都係咁 啲黑社會收錢嚟破壞<br />\n<br />\n如果唔支持中共嗰啲 會畀中共鬥 <br />\n<br />\n撈得偏 大把痛腳喺共產黨手上面 同湯渣驊一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢班人唔係普通市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以根本冇太大嘅民意流失 唔使擺喺心上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n影呢啲人相 起埋底 睇下佢哋係咩人咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種人逃稅 漏稅 走私 運毒咩都做 到時咪做良好市民 打擊犯罪囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8a593bd34d65ed66056cb3fbbb4f19aae0c40e","tid":1268352,"uid":45206,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"當年仲有啲原居民好多都係黑社會<br />\n聽講一車車過嚟打佔中啲人<br />\n原居民應該好多人都識 要起底應該唔係好難？"},{"pid":"716255dc079675b554478179413a29f84bfcfb7f","tid":1268352,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"749934091c68a5a78df50e77215692a86d2cb9a4","tid":1268352,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"呢D廢物既民意我地唔希罕"},{"pid":"910148424a8a4f985bbf1bc8f845d920f035ef86","tid":1268352,"uid":45206,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"749934091c68a5a78df50e77215692a86d2cb9a4","tid":1268352,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"呢D廢物既民意我地唔希罕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:30:19.000Z","msg":"重點係佢哋唔係真係普通市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二百萬嘅民意其實冇分裂過<br />\n佔中嗰時 就係成日用呢樣嘢嚟分裂啲市民<br />\n真係唔可以中伏囉<img src